      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员几乎排除 7 月降息的可能性，9 月降息前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ecb-officials-all-but-rule-out-july-cut-with-september-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧洲央行官员几乎排除了7月份第二次降息的可能性，部分官员还质疑在9月份的下次会议上采取此举是否明智。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ecb-officials-all-but-rule-out-july-cut-with-september-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:46:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
