      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/cocoa-futures-advance-with-supply-concerns-back-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对供应短缺的担忧再度升温，可可价格在 4 月份上涨至历史新高。]]></description>
