    <item>
      <title>市场综述：欧洲央行“鹰派降息”提振欧元，债券市场止步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲央行在普遍预期的降息后上调了通胀预期，全球债券市场在 2024 年创下最长上涨势头后失去动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 22:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
